  Locus:
    Page: 177
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Friendship
---
We cannot tell the precise moment when friendship is formed. As in filling
a vessel drop by drop, there is at last a drop which makes it run over; so
in a series of kindnesses there is at last one which makes the heart run
over.
